text: (punarut'thana dinada) a ghaligeya jnanavu iruvudu allahana bali matra. Avane maleyannu surisuttane. Garbhagalolage enide embudannu avane ballanu. Nale tanenu madaliruvenembudu yarigu tiliyadu. Tanu yava bhumiyalli sayuvenembudu yarigu tiliyadu. Khanditavagiyu allahane ellavannu ballavanu hagu atyanta jagrtanagiddane
